AboutAbout

I am an IT Support Engineer with 4+ years of experience supporting users across APAC, EMEA, and AMER. At Apptio (an IBM company), I focus on cloud technologies, identity and access management, and system administration.

I have managed end-to-end migrations including devices (Windows & Mac), mailboxes, OneDrive, SharePoint, and networks (Cisco to Fortinet), while supporting enterprise tools such as Slack, Teams, Zoom, VPN, and O365. Consistently, I have achieved high service standards with 98% First Call Resolution and 99% Customer Satisfaction.

Currently, I am building expertise in Site Reliability Engineering and DevOps, with hands-on learning in Azure DevOps, Docker, and Kubernetes.
